    Welcome

    Choosing which school to attend is a decision that will shape you and your future in unimaginable ways. It is a choice that requires careful consideration. As you research and deliberate, please consider Pacific Academy: A school where the passion is palpable, the concern for others is obvious, the academics are top-notch, and the community is close and kind. We do think we make a difference in each child's life, and encourage you to share in this experience.

    Voting in California

    As a voter, you will help decide who will lead us. You make your voice heard on important issues that affect the future of our state and nation. Every time you use your precious right to vote, our democracy grows stronger.
